    <div class="container">
        <header id="header">
            <div class="header-title">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-paw"></i> Nehru Zoological Park</h1>
            </div><br>
            <div class="header-subcontent">
                <p>One of the largest zoos in India with a thrilling safari</p>
                <div class="hyderabad-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Hyderabad, Telangana, India
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="main-image-container">
            <img src="https://holidayszone.in/images/sightseeing-places/hyderabad/headers/nehru-zoological-park-hyderabad-tour-header.jpg"
                alt="Nehru Zoological Park" class="main-image">
            <div class="image-overlay">
                <h2>"A Wildlife Haven"</h2>
                <p>Established in 1963 near Mir Alam Tank</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="description" id="description">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-history"></i> About the Zoo</h2>
            <p>Nehru Zoological Park, established in 1963, is one of the largest zoos in India, located near Mir Alam Tank in Hyderabad. Spanning over 380 acres, it is home to a diverse range of animals, birds, and reptiles, making it a paradise for nature and animal lovers. The zoo also features a thrilling safari park for an immersive wildlife experience.</p>

            <div class="historical-fact">
                Named after India's first Prime Minister, Jawaharlal Nehru, the zoo was created to promote wildlife conservation and education. It houses over 1,500 species, including rare animals like the Indian rhinoceros, Asiatic lion, and Bengal tiger.
            </div>

            <p>The zoo offers attractions like a lion safari, tiger safari, and a nocturnal animal house, along with a toy train for kids and a butterfly park. It is a perfect destination for families, wildlife enthusiasts, and photographers.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; color: var(--hyderabad-blue);"><i class="fas fa-paw"></i> Key Features</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                <li>Over 380 acres with 1,500+ species of animals and birds</li>
                <li>Lion and tiger safari park for an immersive experience</li>
                <li>Nocturnal animal house and butterfly park</li>
                <li>Toy train and children’s play area</li>
                <li>Conservation and educational programs</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <div class="nearby-section">
            <section class="restaurants" id="restaurants">
                <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Nearby Restaurants</h2>

                <div class="restaurant">
