                    <div class="distance"><i class="fas fa-walking"></i> 1 km from Nehru Zoological Park</div>
                    <p>A historic water reservoir built during the Qutb Shahi era, offering peaceful views and a great spot for photography.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="place">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://www.hyderabadtourism.travel/images/places-to-visit/headers/golkonda-fort-hyderabad-tourism-entry-fee-timings-holidays-reviews-header.jpg"
                            alt="Golkonda Fort" class="place-image">
                    </div>
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-archway"></i> Golkonda Fort</h3>
                    <div class="distance"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 4 km from Nehru Zoological Park</div>
                    <p>A historic fort with magnificent architecture, famous for its sound and light show in the evening.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="place">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://www.hyderabadtourism.travel/images/places-to-visit/headers/qutb-shahi-tombs-hyderabad-tourism-entry-fee-timings-holidays-reviews-header.jpg"
                            alt="Qutb Shahi Tombs" class="place-image">
                    </div>
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-monument"></i> Qutb Shahi Tombs</h3>
                    <div class="distance"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 3.5 km from Nehru Zoological Park</div>
                    <p>A historical site featuring the tombs of the Qutb Shahi rulers, with stunning Indo-Islamic architecture.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="place">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://www.hyderabadtourism.travel/images/places-to-visit/headers/taramati-baradari-hyderabad-tourism-entry-fee-timings-holidays-reviews-header.jpg"
                            alt="Taramati Baradari" class="place-image">
                    </div>
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Taramati Baradari</h3>
                    <div class="distance"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> 4 km from Nehru Zoological Park</div>
                    <p>A historic landmark with a beautiful garden and panoramic views of the city, ideal for history enthusiasts and nature lovers.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="place">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://www.hyderabadtourism.travel/images/places-to-visit/headers/salar-jung-museum-hyderabad-tourism-entry-fee-timings-holidays-reviews-header.jpg"
                            alt="Salar Jung Museum" class="place-image">
